@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram (Graderate System)

[*] --> Waiting

state Waiting
Waiting : entry / Initial state

state Active
Active : entry / Rate active

state Expired
Expired : entry / Rate expired

state Archived
Archived : entry / Rate archived

Waiting --> Activate : [Start date arrives]

state "Activate" as Activate {
    [*] --> ValidityPeriod

    state ValidityPeriod
    state "End Validity Period" as EndValidity
    state Expire : [Finish date is reached]

    Activate --> ValidityPeriod : [Start date <= Current date]
    ValidityPeriod --> Expire : [Finish date <= Current date]
    Expire --> Archive : [Current date >= Expiration date + 1 year]

    ValidityPeriod --> Active : [Current date < Finish date]
}

ValidityPeriod : entry / Within validity period
ValidityPeriod : do / Maintain active state

Expire : entry / Rate expired
Expire : do / Mark as expired

Archive : entry / Rate archived
Archive : do / Remove or archive

@enduml
